{
  "stem": "6195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He only ask that we don't go outside, because there will still be Germans hidden somewhere, and to wait till the liberation army comes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We hoped it would be the Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- there were-- yeah, yeah-- the Russians, who treated us worse than the German women, they told us to peel potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the German women were sitting doing nothing in their beautiful homes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the-- that was another story, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "While Schindler is gone, everybody was crying when he waved good-bye.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was-- I was in Poland when he was in Israel, when the Jews brought him to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in his will, you know that he wanted to be buried in Israel with his Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He would-- I think he would be the happiest man to live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- you know how the army, when it's-- occupying or marching into a-- in the-- into a place they have fought for-- since-- I don't know what you call it in English.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew the word, but I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sent first a-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A man, a Russian officer came riding into the yard in-- on a horse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were all excited, of course, but at the same time, afraid, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Russians never appealed to any of us, although there were some that were running with red flags.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even though Schindler said not to leave the camp, somebody was marching through the road-- like from here to the house there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they thought they were the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they ran out waving red flags, and they got shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because there were still Germans running around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, well-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--there was-- when they marched in, he said to us, who are you?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
